try it first.

581
00:40:00,900 --> 00:40:02,500
Let's wait a bit more, all right?

582
00:40:02,500 --> 00:40:04,770
I'm not yet 100% sure.

583
00:40:04,770 --> 00:40:08,149
I promise you it'll be a success soon.

584
00:40:08,150 --> 00:40:09,660
All right?

585
