591
00:40:31,900 --> 00:40:33,180
All right then.

592
00:40:33,180 --> 00:40:34,380
I promise you.

593
00:40:34,380 --> 00:40:39,220
But can I keep it for you for the moment?

594
00:40:39,220 --> 00:40:41,700
When I get the official approval document, I'll give it to you as soon as I can.

595
00:40:41,700 --> 00:40:43,290
Okay?

596
00:40:44,620 --> 00:40:46,230
I don't want it.

597
