Let's make a deal.

602
00:41:01,140 --> 00:41:04,799
Don't you always want me to draw a painting for you?

603
00:41:07,090 --> 00:41:09,290
Now I'll draw it for you.

604
00:41:10,730 --> 00:41:13,280
But this little pill

605
00:41:13,280 --> 00:41:15,970
