00:41:36,950 --> 00:41:39,080
Jiahui, you are here.

607
00:41:39,080 --> 00:41:40,229
Come on in.

608
00:41:40,230 --> 00:41:42,050
I have something for you.

609
00:42:08,120 --> 00:42:11,080
